1. Project Title

Healthbot â€“ Web Based Medical Chatbot Using Python Flask

2. Introduction

Healthbot is a web-based chatbot designed to provide basic medical guidance to users by interacting in a conversational format. The chatbot accepts symptoms from the user and provides preliminary advice using a Python Flask backend.

The system consists of a frontend built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript and a backend developed using Python Flask that processes user queries and returns suitable responses.

This project demonstrates client-server communication, REST API integration, and rule-based chatbot logic.

