7. Working of the System

User opens chatbot interface

User clicks "Get Started"

User enters symptoms (fever, cold, pain etc.)

Message is sent to Flask server

Flask processes message using conditions

Response is sent back as JSON

Chatbot displays medical advice

8. Backend Logic Explanation

The Flask server receives POST requests containing user messages.
Based on keywords, the system determines the response.

Example:

"fever" â†’ asks about temperature

"cold" â†’ suggests rest and warm fluids

"pain" â†’ suggests doctor consultation

