13. Conclusion

Healthbot successfully demonstrates how a chatbot can assist users with basic medical guidance using web technologies and Python backend.

The project combines frontend design with backend logic, showing practical implementation of REST APIs and real-time user interaction.

This system can be further enhanced into a full healthcare assistant using AI technologies.
